snippet.title: Neural Dominion Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Join the Discord: 
https://discord.gg/4SYDDVSM

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2493210/Neural_Dominion/

Pre-Alpha gameplay trailer for Neural Dominion, a brutal cyberpunk 4X turn-based strategy game by GamesBond Studios and Camlann Games. Take control of one of 5 gangs in Technograd — a dark, crime-ridden city where getting to the top is the only thing that matters.

Join the Discord: 
https://discord.gg/ddrAdPsEdd

#cyberpunk #strategygames #pcgaming #indiedev
